<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.1">
<l>koṅka larntama larkku runtamo citta kōvala ṉempirāṉ</l>
<l>caṅku taṅkuta ṭaṅka ṭaltuyil koṇṭa tāmaraik kaṇṇiṉaṉ</l>
<l>poṅku puḷḷiṉai vāypi ḷantapu rāṇart</l>
<l>tammiṭam poṅkunīrc</l>
<l>ceṅka yaltiḷaik kuñcu ṉaittiru vēṅka ṭamaṭai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, take refuge at Tiruvēṅkaṭam with springs</l>
<l rend="indent">where red carp play in swift waters,</l>
<l>The place of the one of the Purāṇa-s who split the mouth of the swift bird,</l>
<l>The lotus-eyed one who sleeps in the vast sea where conch abide, our lord,</l>
<l>The herder who broke the wild lime tree with flowers where pollen spreads.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
